 & =w\left(-\frac{1}{2}\mathrm{trace}\left(\Lambda\theta\theta^{T}\right)+x^{T}\Lambda\theta\right)+\frac{p}{2}\log\left|w\right|+\frac{1}{2}\log\left|\Lambda\right|\textrm{ (here p=2)}\\
